node.text: You guys have been asking me for so long now and I’ve had to keep this secret 🤐 but i can finally say, THE GUYS AND I ARE BACK! Season 3 of @carmastersrusttoriches on @netflix airs August 4th! Make sure you guys tag Netflix and let them know how excited you are, and click the link in my bio to leave comments on the official trailer too 🏁 #carmastersrusttoriches #constancenunes

node.title: Car Masters: Rust to Riches Season 3

node.text: Just two more weeks till the new season of #carmastersrusttoriches airs on @netflix ! Make sure you set your alarms for March 27th so you can check out what we have been up to. For now check the trailer here and the link in my bio...Who can guess which car was my favorite build of the season just off this sneak peak? 😍 #carsbyconstance #constancenunes

node.text:
Had the most amazing time @nhra thanks to @shoeracing 🏁I got to bring my dad down to the starting line, meet with all the amazing team drivers, and of course get to see some badass race cars 🤘🏽 Can’t wait for more events later in the season…good luck out there today to the whole team! #carsbyconstance #constancenunes 

(Wearing @guess @marciano 🖤)

node.text: You guys have been asking me for so long now and I’ve had to keep this secret 🤐 but i can finally say, THE GUYS AND I ARE BACK! Season 3 of @carmastersrusttoriches on @netflix airs August 4th! Make sure you guys tag Netflix and let them know how excited you are, and click the link in my bio to leave comments on the official trailer too 🏁 #carmastersrusttoriches #constancenunes

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Constance Nunes on May 09, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, dog, flower and outdoors.

node.text:
Thankful to be Buff’s mommy today and everyday🥰 This little boy is my whole heart and soul and brings me more joy than i could ever ask for 💕 Happy #mothersday to all the moms, grandmas, pet moms, mothers to be, foster moms and mother figures 💕 #constancenunes #dogmom 

For everyone who will ask...
Dress is from @prettylittlething 
Hair by @hairby.nikole @bellamihairpro 
And yes my grass is turf because when you are as busy as me, lawn care is last on the priority list😅
